high_descs: Turn around to reach the nightstand.
Pick up the cup from the nightstand.
Turn around to walk down the hallway and reach the room at the end and take a left turn to reach the brown table.
Put the cup on the table in front of the lamp.
Turn around to walk out of the room and head to the dresser on the left of the bedroom.
Pick up the cup from the dresser.
Turn around, walk back to the room with the table on the left.
Put the cup on the table next to the other cup.
anns.task_desc: Put two cups on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the bedroom.
Take the cup from the table near the bed.
Then go to the next room.
Put the cup on the table near the lamp.
Then go to the bedroom, there is a table.
Take another cup from the white colored table.
And then go to the next room.
Put the cup on the same table near the first cup.
anns.task_desc: Collect the cups from the bedroom.

high_descs: Turn around.
Take a cup from a sitting place.
Turn back, go left through a hallway to a room and, across the room, to a table.
Place the cup on the table.
Walk back to the room you came from and go to a chest of drawers on the opposite side.
Pick up a cup from the chest of drawers.
Walk back to the table in the other room where you previously left the cup
Put the cup on the table next to the other cup.
anns.task_desc: Put two cups on the table.
